od">The Facts About Whole Blood</a></li><ul><li class="first last leaf menu-mlid-2572"><a href="/en/blood/whats-your-type-events">Blood Typing Events</a></li></ul><li class="leaf menu-mlid-2575"><a href="/en/blood/faqs-whole-blood-donations">FAQs: Whole Blood Donations</a></li><li class="last leaf menu-mlid-2872"><a href="/en/blood/clinic-hours#blood">Blood Clinic Hours</a></li></ul></section><section><h4><a href="/en/blood/donating-platelets">Donating Platelets</a></h4><ul><li class="first leaf menu-mlid-2577"><a href="/en/blood/how-platelet-donation-works">How Platelet Donation Works</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-2578"><a href="/en/blood/hla-platelet-matching">HLA Platelet Matching</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-2579"><a href="/en/blood/faqs-platelet-donations">FAQs: Platelet Donations</a></li><li class="last leaf menu-mlid-2835"><a href="/en/blood/clinic-hours#platelet">Platelet Clinic Hours</a></li></ul></section><section><h4><a href="/en/blood/donating-plasma">Donating Plasma</a></h4><ul><li class="first leaf menu-mlid-2581"><a href="/en/blood/how-plasma-donation-works">How Plasma Donation Works</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-2582"><a href="/en/blood/faqs-plasma-donations">FAQs: Plasma Donations</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-19625"><a href="https://www.blood.ca/en/media/canadian-blood-services-does-not-and-will-not-pay-donors">Paying for Plasma</a></li><li class="last leaf menu-mlid-2789"><a href="/en/blood/clinic-hours#plasma">Plasma Clinic Hours</a></li></ul></section><section><h4><a href="/en/blood/recognition-program">Recognition Program</a></h4><ul><li class="first last leaf menu-mlid-2585"><a href="/en/blood/honouring-our-lifeblood">Honouring Our Lifeblood</a></li></ul></section><li class="last leaf menu-mlid-2559 "><a href="/en/blood/blood-safety">Blood Safety</a></li></ul></section></section>
