lunteer">Becoming a Volunteer</a></li></ul></div><section><h4><a href="/en/volunteers/volunteering-opportunities">Volunteering Opportunities</a></h4><ul><li class="first leaf menu-mlid-12791"><a href="/en/volunteers/volunteering-opportunities-alberta-northwest-territories">Alberta &amp; NWT</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-12789"><a href="/en/volunteers/volunteering-opportunities-atlantic">Atlantic</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-12790"><a href="/en/volunteers/volunteer-opportunities-british-columbia-yukon">British Columbia &amp; Yukon</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-12793"><a href="/en/volunteers/volunteering-opportunities-manitoba-saskatchewan">Manitoba &amp; Saskatchewan</a></li><li class="last leaf menu-mlid-12792"><a href="/en/volunteers/volunteering-opportunities-ontario">Ontario</a></li></ul></section><div><ul><li class="leaf menu-mlid-2356 top-level"><a href="/en/volunteers/volunteer-recognition">Volunteer Recognition</a></li></ul></div><section><h4><a href="/en/partnersforlife">Partners for Life</a></h4><ul><li class="first collapsed menu-mlid-2587"><a href="/en/blood/how-do-i-start-team">How Do I Start a Team?</a><ul></ul></li><li class="collapsed menu-mlid-2588"><a href="/en/blood/how-do-i-join-team">How Do I Join a Team?</a><ul></ul></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-2589"><a href="/en/blood/champion-tool-room">Champion Tool Room</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-2590"><a href="/en/blood/partners-life-results">Partners for Life: Results</a></li><li class="leaf menu-mlid-2736"><a href="/en/blood/our-partners">Our Partners</a></li><li class="last expanded menu-mlid-2596"><a href="/en/blood/young-blood-life">Young Blood for Life</a><ul><li class="first leaf menu-mlid-2598"><a href="/en/blood/national-challenge">National Challenge</a></li><li class="last leaf menu-mlid-2597"><a href="/en/blood/youth-development-champion-program">Youth Development Champion Program</a></li></ul></li></ul></section><div><ul><li class="leaf menu-mlid-13660 top-level"><a href="/